mixin about(title)
  section(class="block about" id="about")
    div(class="block__inner about__inner")
      //- div(class="about__title about__title--big title") Что такое Poster?
      h2(class="about__title title")=title

      div(class="about__container")
        div(class="about__body text")
          p Poster kafe buxgalteriya tizimi bu biznes uchun to'liq echimdir, unga har qanday qo'shimcha uskunani ulash mumkin: tarozi, kassa, shtrix-skaner, bank terminali, oshxonaga "yuguruvchilar" ning printeri yoki buyurtmalar yozilgan ekran va boshqa ko'p narsalar.

          p O'rindiqlar sonidan, menyu elementlaridan va hattoki korxona turidan qat'i nazar, kafe uchun dasturiy ta'minotni o'rnatish uchun maxsus qimmatbaho uskunalar sotib olishning hojati yo'q. Poster oddiy planshetlarda ishlaydi - tizim talablariga mos birini tanlang va sotishni boshlang.

          p Ofitsiantlarga qulaylik yaratish uchun siz mijozlarga yanada tezroq xizmat ko'rsatish uchun dasturni bir nechta planshetlarga o'rnatishingiz mumkin.

        div(class="about__image")
          img(src="./assets/images/devices-ru-rub.png", alt="Poster haqida")

    div(class="about__content" id="about-content")
      h2(class="block__inner title about__title about__title-list") Kafeingizni Poster bilan boshqaring
      ul(class="block__inner about__list")
        each item in aboutList
          li(class="about__item")
            div(class="about__icon")
              img(src=item.image, class="about__icon-image" width="100" alt="")
            div(class="about__description")
              h2(class="about__name")=item.name
              div(class="about__text") 
                p=item.text